?GMXL WTP-Space
GMXLOGIT;lhs=y;
    choices=one,two,neither;
    Par;halton;pts=1000;pds=4;Output=IC;wts=wtgend; Tau=0.5;
    ; Fcn = b0(n),MR(n),Job(n),Carbon(n), Cost(*o);
    model:
    U(one)=b0 + MR*MR + Job*Job + Carbon*Carbon + Cost*cost/
    U(two)=b0 + MR*MR + Job*Job + Carbon*Carbon + Cost*cost/
    U(neither)=MR*MR + Job*Job + Carbon*Carbon + Cost*cost$	
?Scenarios WTP (Tables 8)
